name: MIS PIU Cell History for a Prisoner
description:
This report displays the cell location history for a specified prisoner's bookings along with prisoners who have potentially shared a cell with the selected prisoner.
POL0002 v00.00.04 Last Modified: 29/06/16

dataset.name: Cell History
dataset.query: dataset_base_ AS (SELECT AT_BED_ASSIGNMENT_HISTORY.ASSIGNMENT_TIME AS ASSIGNMENT_TIME, AT_BED_ASSIGNMENT_HISTORY.ASSIGNMENT_END_TIME AS ASSIGNMENT_END_TIME, MOVEMENT_TO_ESTABLISHMENT.ESTABLISHMENT_CODE_NK AS ESTABLISHMENT_CODE_NK, AT_OFFENDER_BOOKING_BAH.OFFENDER_ID_DISPLAY AS OFFENDER_ID_DISPLAY, AT_OFFENDER_BOOKING_BAH.SURNAME AS SURNAME, AT_OFFENDER_BOOKING_BAH.MIDDLE_NAME_1 AS MIDDLE_NAME_1, AT_OFFENDER_BOOKING_BAH.GENDER_DESCRIPTION AS GENDER_DESCRIPTION, AT_DOB_DATE.DAY_DATE AS DAY_DATE, AT_OFFENDER_BOOKING_BAH.FIRST_NAME AS FIRST_NAME, AT_OFFENDER_BOOKING_BAH.BOOKING_STATUS AS BOOKING_STATUS, AT_OFFENDER_BOOKING_BAH.BOOKING_NUMBER AS BOOKING_NUMBER, AT_ST_DT.DAY_DATE AS BOOKING_START_DATE, AT_ED_DT.DAY_DATE AS BOOKING_END_DATE, AT_TO_CELL.UNIT_4_DESCRIPTION AS UNIT_4_DESCRIPTION, AT_BED_ASSIGNMENT_HISTORY.LIVING_UNIT_SK AS LIVING_UNIT_SK FROM BODIMIS.FACT_BED_ASSIGNMENT_HISTORY AT_BED_ASSIGNMENT_HISTORY, BODIMIS.DIM_ESTABLISHMENT MOVEMENT_TO_ESTABLISHMENT, BODIMIS.DIM_OFFENDER_BOOKING AT_OFFENDER_BOOKING_BAH, BODIMIS.DIM_DATE AT_DOB_DATE, BODIMIS.DIM_DATE AT_ST_DT, BODIMIS.DIM_DATE AT_ED_DT, BODIMIS.DIM_CELL AT_TO_CELL WHERE (AT_BED_ASSIGNMENT_HISTORY.LIVING_UNIT_SK = AT_TO_CELL.UNIT_4_SK (+)) AND (AT_TO_CELL.ESTABLISHMENT_SK = MOVEMENT_TO_ESTABLISHMENT.ESTABLISHMENT_SK (+)) AND (AT_OFFENDER_BOOKING_BAH.OFFENDER_BOOKING_SK = AT_BED_ASSIGNMENT_HISTORY.OFFENDER_BOOKING_SK) AND (AT_DOB_DATE.DATE_SK = AT_OFFENDER_BOOKING_BAH.BIRTH_DATE_SK) AND (AT_ST_DT.DATE_SK = AT_OFFENDER_BOOKING_BAH.BOOKING_BEGIN_DATE_SK) AND (AT_ED_DT.DATE_SK = AT_OFFENDER_BOOKING_BAH.BOOKING_END_DATE_SK) AND (AT_OFFENDER_BOOKING_BAH.OFFENDER_ID_DISPLAY = (SELECT PRISONER_NUMBER FROM prompt_ /* = #prompt('Enter NOMS Number','A',,Mono,Free,Not_Persistent,,User:0) */) AND AT_TO_CELL.UNIT_4_DESCRIPTION <> 'Not Applicable')), dataset_ AS (SELECT ASSIGNMENT_TIME, ASSIGNMENT_END_TIME, ESTABLISHMENT_CODE_NK, OFFENDER_ID_DISPLAY, SURNAME, MIDDLE_NAME_1, GENDER_DESCRIPTION, DAY_DATE, FIRST_NAME, BOOKING_STATUS, BOOKING_NUMBER, BOOKING_START_DATE, BOOKING_END_DATE, UNIT_4_DESCRIPTION, LIVING_UNIT_SK FROM dataset_base_)

field.name: ASSIGNMENT_END_TIME
field.display: Movement Assignment End Date and Time (Internal)

dataset.name: MIS Load Log
dataset.query: dataset_base_ AS (SELECT DISTINCT BODIMIS.ETL_LOAD_LOG.BUSINESS_DATE AS BUSINESS_DATE FROM BODIMIS.ETL_LOAD_LOG WHERE (BODIMIS.ETL_LOAD_LOG.LOAD_ID = (SELECT MAX(LOAD_ID) FROM BODIMIS.ETL_LOAD_LOG WHERE NOT LOAD_END_DATETIME IS NULL))), dataset_ AS (SELECT BUSINESS_DATE FROM dataset_base_)

dataset.name: Sharers
dataset.query: DP4_ AS (SELECT AT_BED_ASSIGNMENT_HISTORY.ASSIGNMENT_TIME AS ASSIGNMENT_TIME, AT_BED_ASSIGNMENT_HISTORY.ASSIGNMENT_END_TIME AS ASSIGNMENT_END_TIME, MOVEMENT_TO_ESTABLISHMENT.ESTABLISHMENT_CODE_NK AS ESTABLISHMENT_CODE_NK, AT_OFFENDER_BOOKING_BAH.OFFENDER_ID_DISPLAY AS OFFENDER_ID_DISPLAY, AT_OFFENDER_BOOKING_BAH.SURNAME AS SURNAME, AT_OFFENDER_BOOKING_BAH.MIDDLE_NAME_1 AS MIDDLE_NAME_1, AT_OFFENDER_BOOKING_BAH.GENDER_DESCRIPTION AS GENDER_DESCRIPTION, AT_DOB_DATE.DAY_DATE AS DAY_DATE, AT_OFFENDER_BOOKING_BAH.FIRST_NAME AS FIRST_NAME, AT_OFFENDER_BOOKING_BAH.BOOKING_STATUS AS BOOKING_STATUS, AT_OFFENDER_BOOKING_BAH.BOOKING_NUMBER AS BOOKING_NUMBER, AT_ST_DT.DAY_DATE AS BOOKING_START_DATE, AT_ED_DT.DAY_DATE AS BOOKING_END_DATE, AT_TO_CELL.UNIT_4_DESCRIPTION AS UNIT_4_DESCRIPTION, AT_BED_ASSIGNMENT_HISTORY.LIVING_UNIT_SK AS LIVING_UNIT_SK FROM BODIMIS.FACT_BED_ASSIGNMENT_HISTORY AT_BED_ASSIGNMENT_HISTORY, BODIMIS.DIM_ESTABLISHMENT MOVEMENT_TO_ESTABLISHMENT, BODIMIS.DIM_OFFENDER_BOOKING AT_OFFENDER_BOOKING_BAH, BODIMIS.DIM_DATE AT_DOB_DATE, BODIMIS.DIM_DATE AT_ST_DT, BODIMIS.DIM_DATE AT_ED_DT, BODIMIS.DIM_CELL AT_TO_CELL WHERE (AT_BED_ASSIGNMENT_HISTORY.LIVING_UNIT_SK = AT_TO_CELL.UNIT_4_SK (+)) AND (AT_TO_CELL.ESTABLISHMENT_SK = MOVEMENT_TO_ESTABLISHMENT.ESTABLISHMENT_SK (+)) AND (AT_OFFENDER_BOOKING_BAH.OFFENDER_BOOKING_SK = AT_BED_ASSIGNMENT_HISTORY.OFFENDER_BOOKING_SK) AND (AT_DOB_DATE.DATE_SK = AT_OFFENDER_BOOKING_BAH.BIRTH_DATE_SK) AND (AT_ST_DT.DATE_SK = AT_OFFENDER_BOOKING_BAH.BOOKING_BEGIN_DATE_SK) AND (AT_ED_DT.DATE_SK = AT_OFFENDER_BOOKING_BAH.BOOKING_END_DATE_SK) AND (AT_OFFENDER_BOOKING_BAH.OFFENDER_ID_DISPLAY = (SELECT PRISONER_NUMBER FROM prompt_ /* = #prompt('Enter NOMS Number','A',,Mono,Free,Not_Persistent,,User:0) */) AND AT_TO_CELL.UNIT_4_DESCRIPTION <> 'Not Applicable')), dataset_base_ AS (SELECT AT_BED_ASSIGNMENT_HISTORY.ASSIGNMENT_TIME, AT_BED_ASSIGNMENT_HISTORY.ASSIGNMENT_END_TIME, AT_TO_CELL.UNIT_4_DESCRIPTION, MOVEMENT_TO_ESTABLISHMENT.ESTABLISHMENT_CODE_NK, AT_OFFENDER_BOOKING_BAH.OFFENDER_ID_DISPLAY, AT_OFFENDER_BOOKING_BAH.SURNAME, AT_OFFENDER_BOOKING_BAH.FIRST_NAME, AT_OFFENDER_BOOKING_BAH.MIDDLE_NAME_1, AT_DOB_DATE.DAY_DATE FROM BODIMIS.FACT_BED_ASSIGNMENT_HISTORY AT_BED_ASSIGNMENT_HISTORY, BODIMIS.DIM_CELL AT_TO_CELL, BODIMIS.DIM_ESTABLISHMENT MOVEMENT_TO_ESTABLISHMENT, BODIMIS.DIM_OFFENDER_BOOKING AT_OFFENDER_BOOKING_BAH, BODIMIS.DIM_DATE AT_DOB_DATE WHERE ( AT_BED_ASSIGNMENT_HISTORY.LIVING_UNIT_SK=AT_TO_CELL.UNIT_4_SK(+) ) AND ( AT_TO_CELL.ESTABLISHMENT_SK=MOVEMENT_TO_ESTABLISHMENT.ESTABLISHMENT_SK(+) ) AND ( AT_OFFENDER_BOOKING_BAH.OFFENDER_BOOKING_SK=AT_BED_ASSIGNMENT_HISTORY.OFFENDER_BOOKING_SK ) AND ( AT_DOB_DATE.DATE_SK=AT_OFFENDER_BOOKING_BAH.BIRTH_DATE_SK ) AND ( AT_BED_ASSIGNMENT_HISTORY.LIVING_UNIT_SK IN (SELECT LIVING_UNIT_SK FROM DP4_ ) AND AT_OFFENDER_BOOKING_BAH.OFFENDER_ID_DISPLAY <> (SELECT PRISONER_NUMBER FROM prompt_ /*= #prompt('Enter NOMS Number','A',,Mono,Free,Not_Persistent,,User:0) */ ) AND ( exists ( select 1 from bodimis.fact_bed_assignment_history fbah inner join bodimis.dim_offender_booking dob on fbah.offender_booking_sk = dob.offender_booking_sk where fbah.living_unit_sk = at_bed_assignment_history.living_unit_sk and trunc(fbah.assignment_time) <= coalesce(trunc(at_bed_assignment_history.assignment_end_time), sysdate) and coalesce(trunc(fbah.assignment_end_time), sysdate) >= trunc(at_bed_assignment_history.assignment_time) and fbah.living_unit_sk > 0 and dob.offender_id_display = @variable('Enter NOMS Number') ) ) )), dataset_ AS (SELECT  FROM dataset_base_)
